{"about_the_game":"Return home and uncover the mystery of your daughter's death, and the demon that plagues you, in this escape room style atmospheric puzzler.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Key Features</h2><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Atmospheric Horror</li></ul>A greater focus on atmosphere and building tension rather than cheap scares.<br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Discover the Mystery</li></ul>Read notes and explore the house to uncover the dark history of our protagonist.<br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Engaging Puzzles</li></ul>Simple yet satisfying environmental puzzles help to move the game along and engage the player without distracting from the horror.<br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Unique Mechanics</li></ul>Interesting features such as a real time instant film camera, and usable VHS player contribute to making old ideas feel fresh.","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1996760/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1684768882","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1996760/page.bg.jpg?t=1684768882","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1996760/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1684768882","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1996760/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1684768882","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2},{"description":"Family Sharing","id":62}],"content_descriptors":{"ids":[5],"notes":"Contains brief violence, alcohol abuse, and references to other adult themes, including domestic abuse and suicide."},"detailed_description":"<h1>Thank you!</h1><p>Thank you for supporting my first video game! I started making this to learn visual coding in Unreal Engine, and begin my game development journey. It's short (20-40 minutes average playtime), but a good pass time for those who enjoy atmospheric horror, or want a light introduction to the horror video game genre. I am always looking for ways to improve, so constructive criticism is welcome. Thank you for playing and being apart of my journey!</p><br><h1>About the Game</h1>Return home and uncover the mystery of your daughter's death, and the demon that plagues you, in this escape room style atmospheric puzzler.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Key Features</h2><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Atmospheric Horror</li></ul>A greater focus on atmosphere and building tension rather than cheap scares.<br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Discover the Mystery</li></ul>Read notes and explore the house to uncover the dark history of our protagonist.<br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Engaging Puzzles</li></ul>Simple yet satisfying environmental puzzles help to move the game along and engage the player without distracting from the horror.<br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Unique Mechanics</li></ul>Interesting features such as a real time instant film camera, and usable VHS player contribute to making old ideas feel fresh.","developers":["Violet Angel Interactive"],"genres":[{"description":"Adventure","id":"25"},{"description":"Indie","id":"23"}],"header_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1996760/header.jpg?t=1684768882","is_free":false,"linux_requirements":{"minimum":"<strong>Minimum:</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"></ul>","recommended":"<strong>Recommended:</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"></ul>"},"mac_requirements":{"minimum":"<strong>Minimum:</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"></ul>","recommended":"<strong>Recommended:</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"></ul>"},"movies":[{"highlight":true,"id":256885907,"mp4":{"480":"http://video.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_trailers/256885907/movie480.mp4?t=1652298802","max":"http://video.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_trailers/256885907/movie_max.mp4?t=1652298802"},"name":"Penitence Official Trailer 2022","thumbnail":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/256885907/movie.293x165.jpg?t=1652298802","webm":{"480":"http://video.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_trailers/256885907/m